docs.lead_paragraph: [Per lsatel at Charleston] EXCHANGE--NEW-York, Baltimore, Boston, Charleston and Philadelphia, 5263, premium for 60 days. FREIGHTS--To Poits north of Hatteras, 11/2 ? box Sugar: 51/2 ? hogshead Sugar; 31/2 @1? hogshend Molasses. There have been several arrivals of large vessels, but they are not in demand--smaller vessels having the preference.

docs.lead_paragraph: FURTHER ISSUE OF CENTRAL PARK STOCK--MISCELLANEOUS BUSINESS. The Mayor sent a Message to the Board of Aldermen last evening, in which he assigns his reasons for declining to approve the appointment of any more Commissioners of Deeds; he says there are 340 persons exercising the duties of the office in this City, while by law only 300 are allowed.
